---
title: General Tso Chicken Breast Sandwiches with Roasted Potato Rounds and Sriracha Mayo
description: The perennial favourite Chinese dish in sandwich form! Juicy chicken breasts are slathered with that sweet, tangy sauce we all know and love, and there's a sriracha mayo for dipping the roasted potato rounds into!
